<item>
            <title>[BEAM-2190] User depending on IO-GCP still gets a dependency on protobuf-lite</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/BEAM-2190</link>
                <project id="12319527" key="BEAM">Beam</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Somehow a user with a single dependency on &lt;tt&gt;org.apache.beam:beam-sdks-java-io-google-cloud-platform&lt;/tt&gt; gets a transitive dependency on &lt;tt&gt;protobuf-lite&lt;/tt&gt;, despite it being banned in our build and excluded from &lt;tt&gt;grpc-protobuf-lite&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We must need to do more work.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
